<cb:div type="cbeta-notes">
<head>CBETA 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0558b13" resp="#resp3" type="mod_biao" target="#nkr_note_mod_biao_0558b13">忿競生乎眾聚無諍出乎空閑<choice cb:resp="#resp2"><corr>己</corr><sic>巳</sic></choice>行不脩安能解彼故起脩行</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0556b12" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b12">彌勒既紹尊位又當于此土而成佛眾情所宗故先命之</note>
<note n="0556b13" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b13">無生法忍即不退轉地之行也</note>
<note n="0556b14" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0556b14">菩提者彼語有之此無名也實則體極居終智慧也然有三品聲聞也辟支佛也佛也二乘各以其道為菩提耳唯佛菩提為無上正徧</note>
<note n="0557b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0557b01">彌勒向說行意以受記引之耳不為說受記也彼生著情便貪說以存行見菩提可得也</note>
<note n="0557b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0557b02">玄言奧旨妙義微情真出世間之見出世間之文也</note>
<note n="0557b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0557b03">菩提者正覺無相之真智乎虗玄無相不可為有用之彌勒不可為無不知所以言故強名曰菩提斯無為之道豈可以身心得乎</note>
<note n="0557b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0557b04">無異者萬法同體是非一致不異惟菩提乎</note>
<note n="0557b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0557b05">菩提無知而無所不知故微妙難知也</note>
<note n="0557b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0557b06">光嚴雖欲得道場而未知所以得得必由因故為廣說萬行萬行是道場因而言道場者因中說果也</note>
<note n="0557b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0557b07">直心無虗假斯乃基萬行之本但進道之場以下三十二處備列諸行盡是脩心閑地弘道淨場也</note>
<note n="0557b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0557b08">慈生愛愛生著著生累累生悲悲生憂憂生惱惱生憎慈悲雖善而累想生故兩捨以平等觀謂之捨行</note>
<note n="0557b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0557b09">四攝事皆攝眾生齊歸于道也道品斷受生故名捨有為亦以空空三昧及一切善法故名捨也</note>
<note n="0557b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0557b10">行則遊道場止則住佛法舉止無非道場矣</note>
<note n="0557b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0557b11">波旬秦言殺者常欲斷人慧命亦名惡中惡</note>
<note n="0558b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0558b01">憍尸姓也字摩迦陀</note>
<note n="0558b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0558b02">堅法三堅法也去封累而脩道必獲身無極命無窮財無盡故名堅法</note>
<note n="0558b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0558b03">低頭一視仰面一觀</note>
<note n="0558b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0558b04">天女樂五欲而居士以法樂進隨病付藥正如此</note>
<note n="0558b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0558b05">三脫空無相無作也縛以之解謂之脫三乘所由謂之門不盡其極而中路取證謂之非時此大士所不樂也</note>
<note n="0558b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0558b06">因事與願菩薩常法以女還魔魔願具足故因以生願願一切眾生得法願具足</note>
<note n="0558b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0558b07">後世傳燈之說始于此</note>
<note n="0558b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0558b08">無盡燈三字傳至于今而彌昌彌熾彌融彌朗所化獨諸女乎哉自在神力直至無垠矣</note>
<note n="0558b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0558b09">大施會婆羅門法七日祀梵天行大施期生彼承嫡繼業於父舍然也施之大矣</note>
<note n="0558b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0558b10">施有三種一財施二心施三法施以財施人名為布施慈心等心與人樂名為心施說法利人名為法施</note>
<note n="0558b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0558b11">遠離有二種身棲事表名身遠離心無累想名心遠離身心不著亦以名離</note>
<note n="0558b12" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0558b12">無相則絕有為故誨令不舍也</note>
<note n="0558b13" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0558b13">忿競生乎眾聚無諍出乎空閑巳行不脩安能解彼故起脩行</note>
<note n="0559b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0559b01">一切智慧即智業也一切善法即德業也助佛道法大乘諸無漏法也</note>
<note n="0559b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0559b02">曰分作二分者欲明等也現神力騐法施也變寶臺豈財施能為乎法施會然也故無不周耳若齊尊卑一行報以平等悲而為施者乃具足發（發疑法）施耳</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
